HISTORY - SGK

2.1.0

  * consolidated Makefile(s) to build the code

  * fixed is_bad.f to work w/ pgfortran, ifort and pgf77

  * fixed other minor inconsistencies to allow compilation w/ all 3 compilers
    
  * included scripts
    extract  pandora  pmerge  ready
    pgfortran, ifort and pgf77 versions of pandora and ready

  * checked that it builds and run all 6 demos with

     pgfortran -g -C
     pgfortran, pgfortran -O, pgfortran -fast
     ifort, ifort -O, ifort -O4
     pgf77, pgf77 -O, pgf77 -fast

  * ran all demos

    1 2 3 4 5 6

  * wrote this file and the file DETAILS

2.1.1

  * new version of cents.x (cent.f) that uses a file to list the ions
    (ions.list)

  * added support for

     census   (consolidated script to run census)
     census.x (census.f executable)
     lookat.x (RL's lookat.f executable)

  * added a demo for census

     demo/7

  * consolidated scripts to use one setup file (bin/setFORx.sou) to link f77
    LU to names for different compilers (FORnnn vs FORTn)

  * updated documentation files
     DETAILS, README and HISTORY
     demos/HOWTO

